title: JD Wetherspoons
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, International, Beer/Wine, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Chain restaurant offering cheap, pub grub type of food. Many vegetarian items as well a few vegan suitable ones like the freedom salad, and on Thursday a spinach, chickpea, sweet potato curry which is vegan when ask to omit/replace naan bread (contains dairy).
